WEBVTT

00:00:00.405 --> 00:00:02.317
Track 04.06

00:00:04.349 --> 00:00:05.650
BOB: Hi, Kerry.

00:00:05.706 --> 00:00:06.675
KERRY: Hello Bob.

00:00:07.134 --> 00:00:10.443
It’s so nice to see you! How are you?

00:00:10.468 --> 00:00:11.785
BOB: I’m fine, thanks.

00:00:12.299 --> 00:00:14.526
I’m a student at London University now.

00:00:14.551 --> 00:00:15.439
KERRY: Really?

00:00:15.999 --> 00:00:17.549
What subject do you study?

00:00:17.773 --> 00:00:18.506
BOB: Business.

00:00:18.817 --> 00:00:19.781
KERRY: Do you like it?

00:00:19.835 --> 00:00:20.863
BOB: I love it.

00:00:21.246 --> 00:00:22.321
KERRY: And where do you live?

00:00:22.686 --> 00:00:23.503
BOB: In a house with

00:00:23.563 --> 00:00:25.768
two other students. And you?

00:00:26.113 --> 00:00:27.956
KERRY: I live in Hong Kong now

00:00:28.285 --> 00:00:31.248
and I work in an office at the university.

00:00:31.310 --> 00:00:33.902
BOB: Really? Do you speak Chinese?

00:00:33.927 --> 00:00:36.868
KERRY: Well, I have Chinese classes.

00:00:37.236 --> 00:00:39.149
My Chinese isn’t very good,

00:00:39.370 --> 00:00:40.931
but I speak English at work.

00:00:41.195 --> 00:00:43.285
BOB: So why are you in England now?

00:00:43.454 --> 00:00:44.803
KERRY: I’m on holiday.

00:00:45.067 --> 00:00:46.642
I’m here to see my family.

00:00:46.812 --> 00:00:47.967
BOB: How are your mum and dad?

00:00:48.029 --> 00:00:49.678
KERRY: They’re well, thanks.

00:00:49.996 --> 00:00:51.442
How are your parents?

00:00:51.583 --> 00:00:52.456
BOB: They’re fine.

00:00:52.785 --> 00:00:55.412
They live in France now, near Paris.

00:00:55.536 --> 00:00:58.719
KERRY: Wow, that’s great. Hey, look,

00:00:59.056 --> 00:01:04.198
is that Ali over there? Ali! … Ali! …